(977, 109, 'our_solutions_0_solution_description', 'io-market\'s EDI interface enables companies to send and receive business data, such as purchase orders, in a structured, machine-readable format. This means that the incoming order can be transferred directly into the system and executed without further processing, and without the need to manually enter and file the order in advance. This solution works for all paper-based business transactions, such as invoices, delivery bills, order confirmations, etc.'),
