(1368, 111, '_our_solutions_5_solution_title', 'field_60d579661a0b0'),
(1369, 111, 'our_solutions_5_solution_description', 'eBill is the digital bill for Switzerland and Liechtenstein. With eBill, customers no longer receive bills by mail or e-mail, but directly into e-banking - exactly where they are paid. With just a few clicks, bills can be checked and paid while always maintaining complete control. Thanks to eBill, customers pay more reliably, paper consumption is reduced and security is increased.\r\n'),
