(1488, 9, 'history_desc', 'With daily deadlines and pressure, employees require an effective infrastructure to de-stress themselves. The workplace should not only be pleasing to the eyes but it should also be pleasing to the mental health of the employees. We are benefited of having a good infrastructure at our office thereby marking following points as ticked off. \r\nIt will help our employees to boost their productivity. It will make our business more profitable. It will increase peace and tranquillity at the workplace. It will reduce the stress. It will make our employees work hard. As a result it will wipe off the Monday blues of the employees making the office a happy place to work.\r\n'),
