(1504, 9, 'offer_description', '<p>We offer every employee the opportunity to develop and contribute his or her ideas and suggestions. The iomarket India team is working hard on its tasks, but is equally glad to share the successes within the team. Thus, teamwork assumes topmost priority in our company. We can create sustainable solutions only if we all stand together for our values.</p>\r\n<p>iomarket India is expected to grow and as a matter of course, we are looking for people with passion for Internet technology. Does this appeal you and do you wish to join a team that values your opinion and is accustomed to working in a pleasant atmosphere and trustworthy group? Then send us your application including CV, photo and references by email to: <a href=\"mailto:careers@iomarket.in\">careers@iomarket.in</a></p>\r\n'),
