(5961, 348, 'main_sol_add_short_detail', '<p class=\"fs-5\">ColdFusion provides us with a flexible, versatile and browser-based technology to b.dendeliver complete high-end business applications in a very short time. io-market AG Europe had already been relying on the ColdFusion technology right from the start and the solid experience gathered in these years would, of course, be of benefit to our projects. To create the ColdFusion frameworks, we use both Machii – the first object-oriented framework for ColdFusion programming – and ORM – a conceptual modelling technique for databases.</p>\r\n<p class=\"fs-5\">ColdFusion successfully integrates server, database technologies as well as browser functionality into web applications. As an outcome, you can build scalable, data-rich and interactive business applications. However, for enjoying the advantages associated with this platform, you will need to rely on highly skilled experts capable of extracting maximum value from the platform.</p>'),
